	<h1>About Mentorship</h1>
	<div class="text5">
		<p>The Cree Youth Mentor Program is a proactive and unique, online social networking tool exclusively for the Cree Youth. This program provides the opportunity to seek expertise regarding careers, support and guidance from successful and experienced mentors.</p>
		<p>It is a relationship between a mentor and a mentee that is based on mutual trust and respect. This relationship can provide potential internships, job shadowing and possible employment that are only attainable through the connections of the mentor.</p>
	</div>
	<p class="text1">Overall, the Cree Youth Mentor Program is a space to learn and share.</p>

	<h1>Benefits of Mentoring</h1>
	<div class="text5">
		<p>This mentor program is designed to benefit the mentees by providing insight and education towards becoming the person you want to be. Other benefits include:</p>
	</div>
	<div>
		<ul class="list">
			<li>help set career goals and steps to realize them</li>
			<li>access to a support system during critical stages of career development</li>
			<li>exposure and insight from personal experiences</li>
			<li>learn specific skills and knowledge that are relevant to personal growth</li>
			<li>critical feedback</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
